theme_override_font_sizes/font_size = 15
text = "SITE ECHO 7 — CONTROLS

Mouse  — spin to aim (you don't move)
Click  — fire
R      — reload
1-6    — weapon slot
Q      — next weapon
ESC    — pause

LOOP
- Kill zombies → tokens drop
- Wave ends → draft a research note
  (card permanently buffs a weapon)
- Then visit the shop to spend tokens
  on ammo, repairs, or emplacements

OUT OF AMMO? — switch to slot 4
(sidearm, weaker but infinite reserve)

LOW HP? — barrier alarm starts at 25%

You die when the barrier hits 0.
20 waves to clear. Director on wave 20.

(panel fades after 5 kills)"
